ory just like call of duty though there are some mysteries the community must uncover length  long  i think the campaign is about 20 hours long optimization  910  there is alot of optimization you can even switch colors of the teams dlc  medium  there are 3 dlcs at the moment some people think its way to expensive 1399  for 2 helicopters but they always put alot of detail and work into them and a platform update also gets released fair price  yes  final result  97100
