not recommended
i can not in all honesty recommend this game to anyone and heres why  its 32bit  in the most simplest terms this means the game can only use a maximum of 2gb of ram there are other restrictions to this but this is the one that hurts performance the most  multithreading this should have been a priority during development but instead it almost seems like bohemia forgot about this it is poor and extremely bottlenecked resulting in low performance realism  a lot of people go on and on about the realism in vanilla there is only a basic and i mean basic bullet drop system no realistic ballistics whatsoever without the use of mods you could literally be in one of the biggest thunderstorms the game could throw at you with gales rain and all the other lovely things and you will still be able to drop a target at close to a mile away with a precise headshot simply by pointing up a bit there are quite literally dozens of examples of how this game is not realistic heres just a few  vehicle behaviour  is a joke choppers have been updated in the choppers dlc to be more realistic but even then that means you have 2 completely different flight models for vanilla choppers vs vanilla jets obviously they are different one is a chopper the other is a fixed wing jet but heres what i mean choppers now take into account wind speed direction variable gusts as well as reaction forces mostly to do with real world physics and all manner of other things whereas the jets simply dont they feel like they are on rails there is no real skill involded unless dogfighting in flying them ground vehicles are just as bad there was a more realistic driving model in the original grand theft auto and that is the nicest thing i could say about it  low res vs high res players  this admittedly is a multiplayer pvp issue so wont affect pve or sp gameplay but ill try to explain it in pvp if you play pvp you will notice your getting sniped even though your behind a bush or shot through a fence or something similar this is because low res players cant see these details because it is too far away and not yet drawn for them but they can see you this is because the draw distance for a character is permanent and unchangeable it does change but cant be changed by the player without mods whereas the detail draw can be changed through changing settings this is in case you wish to improve performance but this inherently means if you play pvp you have to play with everything turned down just to be on a level playing field not very realistic is it  3rd vs 1st person in pvp multiplayer 3rd person players can see around corners over walls etc whereas 1st person players cant making 1st person in pvp pointless nothing more to say  player animation  this is the thing that really bugs me to the point i have rage quit in the past in what possible universe would a person have to stand still in a firefight just to change weapons there are other animations i detest but that one gets me the most note  this can be fixed with mods  ai behaviour  the ai in this game is a joke and not a funny one they are like headless chickens running around with guns shooting at sounds for example i was playing a game with friends the other night when our pilot was one shotted at over 300m altitude from an ai enemy with a bog standard katiba which is based on a khaybar with its skill setting turned down to 45100 not only was this ridiculous it is also unrealistic i have fired assault weapons irl not a khaybar  unfortunately but i can tell you now there is no way in the entirety of the road to hell could you possibly one shot a pilot in a chopper in the sky flying over 300m at over 80mph with any kind of assault weapon only with a powerful rifle would you even have a chance and even then the shot must be spectacular and ideally head on to the chopper what have i learned from this there is no ballistic shielding simulated in vanilla choppers either in its hull which would be around the cockpit and gunner positions or in the cockpit glass and if it is it is in desperate need of an update i simply refuse to mention ai pilots because they are dead i killed them all for their incompetence ok i know by now your sick of me bashing this beloved game but thats the thing i love this game and like many others i have had hours upon hours of fun playing this but i cannot get past the fact that this game is so unpolished and so poorly optimised it really does feel like a badly made console port and i genuinely feel the same anger i had with gta iv way back when the pc version was first released the random lag or crashing in the middle of the action because the game cant cope with whats going on and just cries in the corner while all the other games just point and laugh at it the reason i portray it that way is because it feels like bohemia is dragging its heels and then when it finally has something to give us it overprices it in what is an apparent need for funds which lets be honest makes them look a bit needy  i can understand that though they need money to pay the staff but what i dont understand is why they give us so little for our money compared to the like of the arma 2 dlcs in which we got factions vehicles soldiers weapons and missions all in one dlc package i know the price was higher but for an example arma 3 helicopters dlc you pay now 08052015 is 1099 gbp or $1695 usd i think anyway what your paying for is the privileged honour of being able to pilot 2 helicopters thats it you get everything else for free in an update including the ability to travel in the helicopters well i suppose thats good right wrong basically they tried to tell us this was some kind of great thing they did for us but in actual fact it was so that it didnt split the playerbase basically covering themselves from flaming on that aspect but i suppose that means most of the people that bought it are going to be decent pilots not all but most yes well yes actually most of the pilots i have flown with flying the dlc choppers are good probably about 70% of time but that means all the really bad pilots vive had in the past all got better at flying or does this mean only the people who bought the dlc were the really good pilots with a few people with spare cash thrown in but if this is the case then bohemia managed to miss out on a massive cash injection by not putting more choppers into the pack maybe even a custom air force faction for nato and csat its only retexturing some uniforms and some code its hardly rocket science it takes time sure but still 2 choppers its an insult i just downloaded a mod which gave me 4 choppers and 7 planes with a custom faction uniforms soldiers equipment etc it took all of 40 seconds to download and hey guess what i didnt spend a penny ok this got way too long way too fast so here conclusion is this i want to recommend this game because i have had a lot of good memories with it and im sure others will like it as well but at the same time i cannot recommend this game for all its flaws if your willing to put serious time into modding this game then yes buy it but as i said i cant recommend this because of it flaws and because of the company behind it i have lost faith in it and cant recommend you buy this to settle confusion my pc  amd fx 8350 black edition 8 core socket am3 40ghz 16mb  4gb xfx radeon r9 290x dd 28nm 5000mhz gddr5 gpu 1000mhz 2816 streams  msi 970 gaming amd970sb950 socket am3  12 gb corsair vengeance ram  850w corsair psu  6x 120mm aerocool shark 15 blade
