todays review arma3 short scorebased review longer review below overall [7390] singleplayer [710]  the game is hard you would do well to save as often as possible multiplayer [810]  its great for multiplayer sadly the ingame browser still lacks refresh button and fails to ever find the server you want to find on a properly forwarded server still stakes 30m  1hour of tinkering for your friends to find it vehicles [ 710]  vehicles are cool plentiful feel well balanced and responsive weapons [910]  lots of weapons with now as added bonus you can customize them multiplayer missions [310]  couple of premade missions most of them proof of concepts no real fun to be had untill you download some from workshop or armaholic i recommend playing my zeus based map which is like playing with a dungeon master who can spawn everything and anything if not that use their awesome easy to use editor and make one yourself editor [610]  it works but doing advanced stuff requires lots of google usage lots of wiki diving and being best friends with the bohemia interactive website also doesnt generate a full mission as it does not include some sort of default descriptionext in the mission file dlc[3340] 1 zeus [1010]  play as a dungeon master make a scenario on the go & its free 2 karting [810]  make races drive in karts and wear the arma 3 karting outfit adds racing elements for race lovers 3 marksman [910]  adds weapons loadouts weaponmods some items facepaint garrage  its good trust me 4 helicopter [610]  adds two helicopters and helicopter pods adds sling loading aka pick stuff up and drop it elsewhere long review below if you have played arma 2 and loved it you will love arma 3 its the same game with better graphics a lot of additions and great changes anyone can just say that though so lets get into some specific as to why arma 3 is a great game for fans of the series and for new players lets start with some points for new players arma 3 is a realistic military combat simulator or that is at least what im going to call it every iteration seems to contain 2 big landmasses one is generally a lot bigger in this case the big landmass youll probably find yourself always playing on is altis its big varied from mountainous to large flats and has a small dessert the game comes with many vehicles for both ground air and water transportation as well as combat we have well known vehicles and newer imaginary versions based on existing vehicles there are also uavs that can be controlled by a single or multiple players as for the gameplay you play as the traditional teams bluefor opfor independant or civilian movement system is great feels very fluid and responsive vehicles can be damaged as a whole or you can shoot out their tiresengine realistic physics allow for some holy  moments no seriously if you have no idea how physics apply to fast moving vehicles this game will teach you by making your car roll over at high speed bends or lets not forget the time i drove a truck on top of a plane hangar because i hit a quadbike then bounced up onto a sand barrier which launched me in the correct angle and with my speed i made it up there then i asked an admin for salvation because falling off was certain death player damage can range from just a fleshwound to holy  my  leg is gone medic if you get shot in a leg you wont be able to run etc 10 for pain uhhhh ahhhh uuuuuuuuhhhh arma 3 is mainly a big sandbox missions can let you roam all of it or just a small ao still you know at all times that everything you see is somewhere you can go almost all buildings can be entered and interestingly with enough explosives almost all of them can be destroyed into nothing but ruble too for veteran players its arma 2 with better graphics and some improvements the old maps can still be played and included with mods warning button bindings make sense now g  grenade i  inventory car mirrors now actually work lots of overhauls to the core game systems helicopters from the dlc pack now can lift cars vehicles boxes ingame server browser is still  arma 3 has a launcher which allows you to play without battleeye if you dont want your computer data compromised no seriously before accepting read the tos for using battleeye i think most people would disagree if they actualy read it you can still play without agreeing to it arma 3 zeus maps aka make your own fun on the go its a sandbox dungeon master its fun try it arma 3 has arma 3 dayz epoch its great try it if you love zombie survival racing is now possible karting and other vehicles too ai are improved no longer  and are deadly at close and long range expect to be fighting them like trained professionals because they will wreck you for the rest its basicly the same as arma 2 i guess simply if you liked arma 2 then buy this one youll love it its worth it thank you for your time
